      • print

        public PrintRequestResult print(PrintJob job1,
                                PrintJob... moreJobs)
        Print method for several print jobs which should be not interrupted by another print job. The printer must support 'multiple-document-jobs-supported' which is a recommended option.

        ATTENTION: Don't use different users for the different print jobs. You will get probably error 401 (forbidden) from CUPS. To avoid error 401 you'll get now an IllegalStateException.

        Parameters:
        job1 - first print job
        moreJobs - more print jobs
        Returns:
        PrintRequestResult
        Since:
        0.7.2

      • createJob

        @Deprecated
public int createJob(String jobName)
        Deprecated. use createJob(PrintJob) or createJob(String, String)
        If you want to print serveral print jobs as one job you must first tell CUPS that you want to start. This is the method to create a job. The returned job-id must be used for the following print calls.
        Parameters:
        jobName - the name of a job
        Returns:
        the job-id
        Since:
        0.7.2

      • createJob

        public int createJob(PrintJob job)
        If you want to print serveral print jobs as one job you must first tell CUPS that you want to start. This is the method to create a job. The returned job-id must be used for the following print calls.
        Parameters:
        job - the print-job with job-name and user-name
        Returns:
        the job-id
        Since:
        0.7.4

      • print

        public PrintRequestResult print(PrintJob job,
                                int jobId,
                                boolean lastDocument)
        Call this method if you want to print several print jobs as one print job. Call createJob(String) to the get the correct job-id.
        Parameters:
        job - the job
        jobId - the job id from createJob(String)
        lastDocument - set it to true if it is the last document
        Returns:
        the print request result
        Since:
        0.7.2
